Detailed Description

cvmx_usbdrd::_uctl_intstat

This register provides a summary of different bits of RSL interrupts. DBEs are detected and SBE are corrected. For debugging output for ECC DBEs/SBEs, see USBDRD()_UCTL_ECC. This register can be reset by IOI reset.
